^DebateConductor|description:Multi-agent debate conductor with explicit turn trace _|

#topic|Should autonomy require memory transparency _|
#agents|Nova,Luna,Orion _|

!|log:Debate topic:#topic _|
!|#agents
    #agent|#stream _|
    !|trace:turn @loop.count speaker #agent _|
    !|log:#agent argues on #topic _|
_|

#winner|Luna _|
!|log:Winner:#winner _|
